name: svelte-coreui-icons
description: Display CoreUI SVG icons in Svelte applications.
readme:
# Svelte Coreui Icons
[Coreui Icons](https://github.com/coreui/coreui-icons) for Svelte. Thank you for considering my open-source package. If you use it in a commercial project, please support me by sponsoring me on [the GitHub sponsor](https://github.com/sponsors/shinokada). Your support helps me maintain and improve this package for the benefit of the community. ## Docs See the [Svelte-Coreui-Icons documentation](https://svelte-coreui-icons.codewithshin.com/) to learn more. ## Icons - [Brand](https://svelte-coreui-icons.codewithshin.com/brand) - [Flag](https://svelte-coreui-icons.codewithshin.com/flag) - [Free](https://svelte-coreui-icons.codewithshin.com/free) ## Repo [GitHub Repo](https://github.com/shinokada/svelte-coreui-icons) ## Installation ```sh pnpm i -D svelte-coreui-icons ``` ## Other icons [Svelte-Icon-Sets](https://svelte-svg-icons.vercel.app/) ## Original source [coreui/coreui-icons](https://github.com/coreui/coreui-icons) ## License [Svelte-Coreui-Icons License](https://github.com/shinokada/svelte-coreui-icons/blob/main/LICENSE) [Coreui-Icons LICENSE](https://github.com/coreui/coreui-icons/blob/main/LICENSE)
